Program: Discovery
Title: Reith Lectures - the triumph of technology - lecture three
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryz0
Last Broadcast Date: 10 May 2005
The second in a series of technology lectures, The third in the series is entitled 'Innovation and Management' and looks at the ways we can move away from the old concepts of science to a new more dynamic inclusive definition and understanding. The Reith Lecture 2005 series is given by Lord Broers, president of the Royal Academy of Engineering and chairman of the House of Lords Science and Technology Committee. Show less